comment: Grant (PHI) does not affect Chandler's (DEN) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Chandler (DEN) and Grant (PHI) make incidental arm to arm contact as Grant attempts to reach in and steal the ball on the drive to the basket.
Chandler (DEN) handchecks Noel (PHI) at the start of his drive and affects his RSBQ.
Chandler (DEN) makes contact with Noel's (PHI) body and the contact affects his play to the basket.
Faried (DEN) does not obtain legal guarding position and makes body to body contact with Canaan (PHI).
Grant (PHI) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly knocks the ball loose from Chandler (DEN) on the drive to the basket.
Foye (DEN) commits a take foul on Canaan (PHI).
Nelson (DEN) purposely makes contact with the ball after the made basket, which prevents the opposing team from quickly inbounding the ball.
Foye (DEN) commits a take foul on Canaan (PHI).
Sampson (PHI) allows Chandler (DEN) to land after the jumpshot.
Faried (DEN) commits a take foul on Covington (PHI).
Correctly called OOB on the missed shot by Lawson (DEN). Philadelphia is awarded possession.
